    • 方法详细资料

      • parseDate

        public static Date parseDate(String lexicalXSDDate)

        Converts the string argument into a date (Date) value.

        参数:
        lexicalXSDDate - A string containing lexical representation of xsd:date.
        返回:
        A date (Date) value represented by the string argument.
        抛出:
        IllegalArgumentException - if string parameter does not conform to lexical value space defined in XML Schema Part 2: Datatypes for xsd:date.

      • printDate

        public static String printDate(Date val)

        Converts a date (Date) value into a string.

        参数:
        val - A date (Date) value
        返回:
        A string containing a lexical representation of xsd:date
        抛出:
        IllegalArgumentException - if val is null.

        public static Date parseDateTime(String lexicalXSDDateTime)

        Converts the string argument into a date/time (Date) value.

        参数:

        返回:
